headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Garage Discounts and More
content:
GTA Online players can take advantage of a range of discounts this week, including 40% off real estate like Garages and Hangars, plus:

Hangar Add-Ons and Modifications - 40% off
Nagasaki Outlaw - 40% off
Karin Sultan Classic - 40% off
Coquette D10 - 40% off

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
